    "long_instructions": "# Loops Practice\r\n\r\nCreate a song using loops. Your song should use at least 3 loops.\r\n\r\n## Validation\r\n\r\n**Success Criteria**\r\n- 3 loops are used anywhere in the song\r\n    - Feedback: \"Nice job! You made a song with at least 3 loops!\":\r\n\r\n**Failure Criteria for additional guidance**\r\n- 2 loops are used\r\n    - Feedback: \"We're only using two loops so far - make sure to add a third!\"\r\n- 1 loop is used\r\n    - Feedback: \"Nice! You're using a loop! Now make sure to use two more!\"\r\n- No loops\r\n    - Feedback: \"It doesn't look like your song uses any loops yet - be sure to add some!\"",
